text: Md. Ghulam Rabbani is an Indian politician serving as Cabinet Minister of State for Labour Government of West Bengal. Rabbani belonging to All India Trinamool Congress. He was elected as MLA of Goalpokhar Vidhan Sabha Constituency in 2011 and 2016. ==References== Category:Living people Category:All India Trinamool Congress politicians Category:Bengali politicians Category:Members of the West Bengal Legislative Assembly Category:1970 births
title: Md. Ghulam Rabbani
